        "subject": "103. 簡介Acker函數，並列出Acker(2,3)的求解過程。",
        "content": "<p>Acker函數又名阿克曼函數，是一種透過遞迴關係所生成的函數。輸入為兩自然數，輸出為一自然數，且其函數值成長幅度巨大，而其反函數主要用於演算法的時間複雜度分析。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>函數定義為<strong>&nbsp;( </strong>以下由A來代指Ackermann function<strong> )</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"A(m,n) = \\begin{cases} n + 1 &amp;\\text{if } m = 0 \\\\ A( m - 1, 1) &amp;\\text{if } m&gt;0 \\ \\&amp; \\ n = 0 \\\\ A(m - 1, A(m,n-1))&amp;\\text{otherwise } \\end{case}\" src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?A%28m%2Cn%29%20%3D%20%5Cbegin%7Bcases%7D%20n%20&amp;plus;%201%20%26%5Ctext%7Bif%20%7D%20m%20%3D%200%20%5C%5C%20A%28%20m%20-%201%2C%201%29%20%26%5Ctext%7Bif%20%7D%20m%3E0%20%5C%20%5C%26%20%5C%20n%20%3D%200%20%5C%5C%20A%28m%20-%201%2C%20A%28m%2Cn-1%29%29%26%5Ctext%7Botherwise%20%7D%20%5Cend%7Bcase%7D\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>常見的Ackermann function有 A(2,2) = 7, A(1,2) = 4, A(2,1) = 5, A(2,3) = 9, A(3,2) = 29</p>\r\n\r\n<p>而A(2,3)的求解過程如下<img alt=\"\" src=\"/user/1/1/11027162/images/305996284_1625712037824417_3373354301334798655_n%20%281%29.jpg\" style=\"height:1439px; width:2048px\" /></p>",
